ardi&amp;publication_year=1993&amp;journal=Cancer&amp;pages=1557-1563&amp;doi=10.1002%2F1097-0142%2819930901%2972%3A5%253C1557%3A%3AAID-CNCR2820720512%253E3.0.CO%3B2-5&amp;pmid=8394197">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">12.</div><div id="r12" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Farinati F, Marino D, De Giorgio M, et al. Diagnostic and prognostic role of alpha-fetoprotein in hepatocellular carcinoma: both or neither? <em>Am J Gastroenterol</em> 2006;101(3):524–532.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1572-0241.2006.00443.x">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16542289/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Diagnostic+and+prognostic+role+of+alpha-fetoprotein+in+hepatocellular+carcinoma%3A+both+or+neither%3F&amp;author=F+Farinati&amp;author=D+Marino&amp;author=M+De+Giorgio&amp;publication_year=2006&amp;journal=Am+J+Gastroenterol&amp;pages=524-532&amp;doi=10.1111%2Fj.1572-0241.2006.00443.x&amp;pmid=16542289">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">13.</div><div id="r13" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Kanematsu M, Semelka RC, Leonardou P, Mastropasqua M, Lee JK. Hepatocellular carcinoma of diffuse type: MR imaging findings and clinical manifestations. <em>J Magn Reson Imaging</em> 2003;18(2):189–195.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/jmri.10336">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12884331/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Hepatocellular+carcinoma+of+diffuse+type%3A+MR+imaging+fin